    IController  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChatController
    This class has full control over the chat views.
    ChooseRobotController
    This class allows the player to choose a figure by clicking on a robot picture
    MapController
    The class MapController notifies the Server where each robot is positioned and and on which tile(type) it rests The mapPane fits the grid and is responsive, furthermore it is zoomable (click the mapPane for requesting focus -> zoom in by pressing "+" / zoom out by pressing "-") and scrollable by Mouse (scroll wheel for y-pos and SHIFT + scroll wheel for x-position) or by keyboard (left by "A" / right by "D" / up by "W" / down by "S").
    OpponentMatController
    This class has full control over the opponentMat views.
    PlayerMatController
    This class has full control over the playermat views.
    ScoreboardController
    This class is responsible for showing the sccoreboard when a player has won the game.
    StageController
    This controller class is responsible for the board and the chat.
    StartScreenController
    This controller class is responsible for showing the startscreen
    WikiController
    This controller class is responsible for the wiki.
